PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years. (Gail Rudderham-Chernin, Sydney, Nova Scotia, in the place of James R. Pat Ellis, whose term has expired; and Charles T. Smith, Arichat, Nova Scotia, in the place of Hugh Tweedie, whose term has expired)
